To show the use of my [woody textures](http://www.gamebanana.com/css/textures/3359 ""), I made this prefab....
==============================================================================================================
Its a nice wooden themed luxury restroom.
-----------------------------------------
It has neon blue, neon pink lighting in the bath tub.
-----------------------------------------------------
### _NOTE: You must have the wooden textures so that the prefab works fine, or else you will face texture errors..._

**Since this prefab has custom textures, don't forget to use PakRat in you map, so that other players don't get texture errors.**

### The Textures are included in the download.
**-Thank You, Matr!X**
